item.title: Hello World
item.description: Hello World! Yet another blog unravels in the depths of the internet. Let’s see if anyone will find it at all :-) If you however do so, you’ll probably read a lot about Windows security, Powershell, AD, privesc and general infosec stuff. Hope you like it stranger!
